title: #195: 5G and Electricity with Sofia Smallstorm and Katrina Lee Franchina
description:
Thank you for tuning in for another episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli. It's Ladies Night today on the podcast as we welcome Sofia Smallstorm and Katrina Lee Franchina to discuss the history of the effects of Electricity on the human body and what's in store for with with the roll out of 5G. You beg for this episode so here you go. Please check out both of these ladies websites.....
Sofia Smallstorm
https://www.aboutthesky.com

Katrina Lee Franchina's Orgonite pyramids, necklaces and charms.
https://www.etsy.com/shop/KatsKrystalShop

Thank you for your support!
